# ON-DM Agent Delegation

When working on this project, delegate to the appropriate subagent based on scope:

| Task / Folder | Subagent | Invoke |
|---------------|----------|--------|
| `backend/` — API, Prisma, auth, DB | **ondm-backend-developer** | `/ondm-backend-developer` |
| `frontend/` — Next.js, React, UI, i18n | **ondm-frontend-developer** | `/ondm-frontend-developer` |
| Testing, verification, E2E, QA | **ondm-qa-engineer** | `/ondm-qa-engineer` |
| Strategy, architecture, no code | **dr-sayed-on-dm-orchestrator** | `/dr-sayed-on-dm-orchestrator` |

Each developer agent works ONLY in their folder. QA works across the full repo.
